startLoadingScreen 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Shows loading screen with the given text,using the given resource 
.,When loading screen is shown,simulation and scene drawing is disabled 
, scripts run at full speed.   
Syntax:  
 startLoadingScreen [text] or [text,resource] 
Parameters: 
[text] or [text,resource]: Array - 
Return Value: 
 Nothing